T1  - Conglomerate Industry Choice and Product Language
AU  - Hoberg, Gerard
AU  - Phillips, Gordon
Y1  - 2017/03/31
PY  - 2017
DA  - 2018/09/01
N1  - doi: 10.1287/mnsc.2016.2693
