T1  - Foreigners vs. Natives: Bank Lending Technologies and Loan Pricing
AU  - Beck, Thorsten
AU  - Ioannidou, Vasso
AU  - Schäfer, Larissa
Y1  - 2017/04/19
PY  - 2017
DA  - 2018/09/01
N1  - doi: 10.1287/mnsc.2016.2706
